{"type": "article", "id": 31196, "title": "阿迪3D打印跑鞋预览，以及，Gap的业绩还在继续跌  | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-08-19T01:48:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 31426, "name": "Carhartt WIP"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 9519, "name": "Thom Browne"}, {"id": 15393, "name": "Perry Ellis"}, {"id": 20739, "name": "STUSSY"}, {"id": 27421, "name": "Beams"}, {"id": 31687, "name": "Gawker Media"}, {"id": 31688, "name": "Ross Stores"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160819091023cwW71fvYSzABo3Vb.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/ross-stores-sales-10510604/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国折扣服装零售集团 Ross Stores 第二季度收入大涨</b></a> | 据 Ross Stores 第二季度财报显示，该集团的净收入上涨了 13%，至 2.82 亿美元。销售额上涨了 7%，至 31.8 亿美元。鉴于不久之前有类似的低价服饰公司大举扩张的消息，美国人看起来最近在买买买上比较保守。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/giorgio-armani-to-sponsor-djokovic-and-friends-gala-charity-dinner-10510567/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Giorgio Armani 将赞助 Novak Djokovic 基金会</b></a> | Giorgio Armani 将成为 Novak Djokovic 基金会和朋友们的晚宴的官方赞助商，该晚宴将于 9 月 20 日在米兰举行。&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\"><b>科技博客&nbsp;<a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/gawker-com-to-close-after-sale-of-gawker-media-to-univision-10510418/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gawker Media 宣布关闭</a></b> | 在美国法院判定传媒集团 Univision 赢得对 Gawker Media 的收购权之后，Gawker 的创始人 Nick Denton 宣布该网站将于下周关闭，他也会退出公司。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/gap-net-down-ceo-peck-cites-turnaround-progress-10510599/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Gap 第二季度收入大跌</b></a> | 由于高昂的重组费用及销售下滑，Gap 集团第二季度收入大跌至 1.25 亿美元，去年同期则为 2.15 亿美元。Gap 预计今年还将关闭 50 家店铺，店铺总面积降低 2%。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>街头品牌 Stüssy 正式推出<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/stussy-2016-lookbook\" rel=\"nofollow\">秋季新品</a>。这个系列的主题依然是纽约和东京，设计上加入了拼接、迷彩等元素。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081909284078ZHs0npBuDfFWOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666097\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819092834F3RzTjC1Dn0hUdrE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666097\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819092828ufb09RoCnSIgyXNU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666097\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Thom Browne 推出宠物狗专属针织衫。选用了最好的羊毛制作，保留了招牌的袖子条纹元素和红白蓝饰边。于纽约和东京的门店出售，定价高达 71000 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819092858FZvhRwNz2jdPTq1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819092852znpA3Uu0GlsXN1v6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Carhartt WIP 联合纽约知名摄影师 Thuan Tran 拍下这<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/carhartt-wip-2016-tale-of-tokyo-wanderers-part-2\" rel=\"nofollow\">「TALE OF TOKYO WANDERERS」</a>造型特辑第二部分正式曝光，该系列将于 9 月上旬登陆亚洲地区各大门店。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819092953tzfT9ba0LulcyZiD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819092946ZPWFmzluvXIitfjE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819092940F3HLYqNlOpGkEJDa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819092923zeJ2DGjNuUwInlh6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819092916gTK4t3XESLOBUGjo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608190929298j7o9A4hanePgIxf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>为庆祝 BEAMS 成立 40 周年，BEAMS 与英国经典的 Dr.Martens 合作，推出了 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/dr-martens-x-beams-1461\" rel=\"nofollow\">1461 系列鞋款</a>。该系列现已登陆 BEAMS 和 Dr.Martens 指定门店。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608191630190exSGV2cYfz7hNHq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819093015NSbQJuhZMvGy9Bed.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819093025BL18RMKdvYt0Q4VW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/8/adidas-futurecraft-on-foot\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Futurecraft 3D 打印跑鞋预览</a>。该系列跑鞋虽然于去年 10 月已经公布，但目前还尚未公开发售。下面是这双跑鞋的上脚效果预览图，看上去外观与 Ultra Boost 非常接近。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819093051n1uMSes65VyU0YqA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819093044GjKRvpmTUz8iEMOZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819093038xIV0w3tFN4SoAuYp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}